   - Build ONE client at module level: `client = TestClient(create_app())`.
   - If the case has a non-empty setup_json, FIRST replay each Arrange call in order against the
     same client to seed state: `for s in json.loads(setup_json): client.post(s.get("route", "<route>"), json=s["inputs"])`.
